data.description: Open and spacious townhome located in gated community. The 2 large bedrooms upstairs have their own baths and walk in closets. Downstairs the kitchen features granite counters and recently updated appliances as well as a 3rd bedroom and 3/4 bath. The backyard was just recently redone with lush green grass and a large patio cover. A brand new HVAC system was just installed last year.
